OL,6,FA young child was injured by shards of
OL,7,Fglass after a "large piece of masonry"
OL,8,Fwas thrown through the window of a
OL,9,Fhouse.
OL,11,FPolice are appealing for information
OL,12,Frelating to a "racially motivated hate
OL,13,Fcrime" in the Roden Street area of
OL,14,Fsouth Belfast on Monday.
OL,16,FDistrict Commander Superintendent
OL,17,FDornan said: "At around 7.40pm on
OL,18,FMonday evening, a large piece of
OL,19,Fmasonry was thrown through a window
OL,20,Finto the living room of a family home.
